### ─── Home (Public) ───

### Home landing data
GET {{baseUrl}}/home

### ─── Anime (Public) ───

### Catalog (default)
POST {{baseUrl}}/anime/search
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Catalog with search
POST {{baseUrl}}/anime/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "q": "That Time I Got Reincarnated as a Slime",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### Catalog with filters
POST {{baseUrl}}/anime/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "genre": "Action",
  "status": "ONGOING",
  "type": "TV",
  "sort": "recent"
}

### Catalog sorted by most viewed
POST {{baseUrl}}/anime/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sort": "most_viewed",
  "page": 1,
  "pageSize": 24
}

### Anime by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto

### ─── Episodes for Upload (UPLOADER, ADMIN) ───

### List episodes with upload status (paginated, 50 per page)
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/that-time-i-got-reincarnated-as-a-slime/episodes?page=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List episodes page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto/episodes?page=2&pageSize=50
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List episodes page 3 (for long anime like One Piece)
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/one-piece/episodes?page=1&pageSize=100
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### ─── Episode detail (Public) ───

### Episode by slug and number (returns embedUrl + language)
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/naruto/episodes/1

### Episode — Tensei Slime ep 1
GET {{baseUrl}}/anime/that-time-i-got-reincarnated-as-a-slime/episodes/2
